source.name: USDA National Nutrient Database for Standard Reference, Release 22
source.description: The USDA Nutrient Database for Standard Reference, Release 22 (SR22) is the major source of food composition data in the United States and provides the foundation for most public and private sector databases.  SR22 contains nutrient data for over 7,500 food items for up to 143 food components, such as vitamins, minerals, amino acids, and fatty acids.  It replaces the previous release,
